OL,3,CPolice share images after eggs thrown
OL,4,Cat LGBTQ venue in suspected hate crime
OL,6,FGloucestershire Police have shared
OL,7,FCCTV images of two children they wish
OL,8,Fto identify following a suspected hate
OL,9,Fcrime in Gloucester.
OL,11,FIt says a group of three teenagers
OL,12,Fthrew eggs at people inside Proud, an
OL,13,FLGBTQ+ venue in Kings Square.
OL,15,FThe incident happened on Wednesday 4
OL,16,FFebruary at around 8pm and police say
OL,17,Fit is being treated as a suspected
OL,18,Fhomophobic hate crime.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
