OL,3,CPolice share images after eggs thrown
OL,4,Cat LGBTQ venue in suspected hate crime
OL,6,FThe force said: "Hate crime and hate
OL,7,Fincidents occur when people are
OL,8,Ftargeted due to their race, religion,
OL,9,Fsexual orientation, transgender
OL,10,Fidentity, or disability.
OL,12,F"Anyone who recognises those pictured
OL,13,Fis asked to contact police online by
OL,14,Fcompleting this form and quoting
OL,15,Fincident 485 of 4 February.
OL,17,F"If you are a victim of hate crime or
OL,18,Fyou have information that could help
OL,19,Fprotect others, you can report it to
OL,20,Fpolice online here."
